rows.label: qst202107_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Shiki.
Shall we head back soon?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0002
rows.name: That's enough already, right?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0003
rows.name: Shiki, let's head back soon, okay?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0004
rows.name:
You've investigated enough,
haven't you?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0005
rows.name:
Shiki.
Shall we head back soon?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0006
rows.name:
We cannot afford to have
too much time taken up here.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0007
rows.name:
Hey, Shiki.
Let's head back soon.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0008
rows.name: You've investigated enough, right?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0009
rows.name:
What are you saying? I have
no intention of moving from here.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0010
rows.name:
If you're going back,
you guys can go back alone.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0011
rows.name: Because I've decided to live here.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0012
rows.name: No, that's not gonna happen!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0013
rows.name: Because we still have things to do!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0014
rows.name: That's no good.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0015
rows.name: Because we still have things to do.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0016
rows.name: I cannot permit that.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0017
rows.name:
There are still things
that we must do.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0018
rows.name:
No, no.
That's not gonna happen either.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0019
rows.name:
There's still a mountain
of things we ought to do.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0020
rows.name:
No way! I hate it!
I'm not going anywhere!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0021
rows.name:
If I don't investigate this place,
who do you think is
going to investigate it?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0022
rows.name:
I have to investigate it for the
sake of everyone living on Alst!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0023
rows.name:
I surrender[ML:Dash ]
Shiki's will is truly firm.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0024
rows.name:
Since it's come to this, you can
investigate until you're satisfied.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0025
rows.name:
Ah~ I give up. When it comes to this,
Shiki absolutely won't break, will she.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0026
rows.name:
Why don't you just investigate
as much as you like?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0027
rows.name:
Good grief. I cannot win
against Shiki's stubbornness.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0028
rows.name:
Understood. You may investigate
until you are satisfied.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0029
rows.name:
You got me, you got me.
It's Shiki's win.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0030
rows.name:
You can investigate until you're
satisfied. However, you gotta help us
out once in a while too, ya hear?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0031
rows.name: Hooray!!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0032
rows.name: As expected of my Driver!!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0033
rows.name:
You're so understanding!
I love that about you!
